{"tid":1945309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【衰過地產商】租戶怒屌機管局一蚊租都唔減！","createTime":"2020-03-27T03:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T05:29:32.000Z","uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6101a28d2eb3ae53c2900c1d7a9be7596bf3a2df","tid":1945309,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"有人以「香港機場一個租戶」署名，於報章登公開信，題為《致特首和司長們：請救救機場商戶》。<br />\n<br />\n信中狠批，港府多次呼籲香港業主減租，與商戶共渡時艱，但由港府全資擁有的機管局，<br />\n<br />\n「在過去兩個月一直無動於衷，繼續收足租金，袋袋平安，你們一邊話『撐企業，保就業』，他們就說『商業決定，在商言商』，對我們的死活置之不理，有行家講得好：『機管局衰過地產商』，真係不無道理。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，信中又指，香港機場租金比IFC、海港城貴，近日機管局提出之措施，亦以航空公司傾斜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機管局於周一公佈，推出10億元援助計劃，有商戶向本報表示要求全面免租，否則將會聯同所有商舖罷市"},{"pid":"6bab97072b99bcaf53fa5b6a1ee219558736802d","tid":1945309,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5410620bca5027985cc78c5f2ad2da2db36bafc","tid":1945309,"uid":11067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"係一個無人嘅地方交住租黎罷市 係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8694439855f621b74c2c81e47eb74c789259195","tid":1945309,"uid":77143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"on99 咁ifc又有無減租啊<br />\n食得鹹魚抵得渴啦，做生意做到輸打贏要肉鳩酸"},{"pid":"e80dbca62cd68b266fd0392338299efab3d59359","tid":1945309,"uid":759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"你而家已經罷緊啦<br />\n唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313d486880fe41fd3add29cba8bc4cd8f42a6134","tid":1945309,"uid":242613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5410620bca5027985cc78c5f2ad2da2db36bafc",